Function to create a rmt_list object from RMODFLOW discete boundary condition object objects

rmti_create_bc_list.Rd

Function to create a rmt_list object from RMODFLOW discete boundary condition object objects

rmti_create_bc_list(obj, conc, itype, kper)

Arguments

obj

RMODFLOW discete boundary condition object. Allowed objects are chd, ghb, riv, drn, wel
conc

vector, data.frame or matrix with concentration values.
itype

integer column (or single value) to indicate flux type
kper

integer value(s) indicating during which stress-periods this rmf_list is active

Value

a rmt_list object
